15
00:01:14.407 --> 00:01:16.201
-[man 3] Here he comes!
-[man 4] He's here!

16
00:01:16.284 --> 00:01:17.410
{\an8}ONE HUNDRED YEARS OF SOLITUDE

17
00:01:17.494 --> 00:01:20.038
[reporters clamoring]

18
