58
00:03:07.312 --> 00:03:08.146
Hello. sir!

59
00:03:08.229 --> 00:03:09.230
{\an8}EPISODE 1

60
00:03:09.314 --> 00:03:10.857
{\an8}How is your knee doing?

61
00:03:10.940 --> 00:03:13.067
{\an8}It's no big deal. It's just a mild sprain.

62
